NSURLSession + Fuzz

This category simplifies the use of NSURLSession for HTTP networking. It aims to reduce the need for third party libraries. Below are areas where this category could be improved



- POST multi-part
- TRACE http method
- CONNECT http method
- Resume download with data
- authentication challenges
- XML Acceptheader

- NSURLSession ephemeral session
- NSURLSession background session
- TLS verification

(from alamofire)
- printable requests
- debug printable
- Output cURL
- UIImageView loadFromURL
- Chainable Requests
- plist parameter encoding
